Introduction

R.Tee, born Kim Jung-gu is a South Korean record producer, songwriter, and DJ who debuted under Cashmere Records in 2014. He is currently signed under the YG subsidiary THEBLACKLABEL. He has produced songs for artists including BIGBANG, BLACKPINK, iKON & WINNER.

His most notable work are "FXXK IT" by BIGBANG, "PLAYING WITH FIRE", "DDU-DU DDU-DU", "Forever Young", "Kill This Love" & "Don't Know What to Do" by BLACKPINK, "Wake Me Up" & "Louder" by Taeyang, "KILLING ME" & "Adore You" by iKON, "Alone" & "Good Luck to You" by Seungri, "The Light" by IMFACT, "BIRTHDAY" by SOMI and "Hold" by WINNER.
